Christophe Paccolat is a PhD student at the Swiss Space Center and Signal Processing Laboratory, working on non-cooperative motion determination for space robotics missions. He received his Master degree from EPFL in 2012 and worked at the Swiss Space Center as Space Engineer for one year before starting his PhD in 2013.

MOOC Responsibility: Teaching Assistant, Exercises
